---
import Layout from "../layout/Layout.astro";
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
import Highlight from "../components/Highlight.astro";
---

<Layout title="About this project">
  <div aria-labelledby="about">
    <p>You're still around? I'm glad.</p>

    <p>
      I originally created this <i>"blogfolio"</i> as a hands-on project while learning
      <Link href="https://astro.build/">Astro</Link>.
    </p>

    <p>
      Here I will practice my writing skills, expand on
      <Link href="/blog/my-philosophy-as-a-dev"
        >my philosophy as a developer</Link
      > and, why not, share some thoughts about life.
    </p>

    <p>Enjoy your stay!</p>

    <br />
    <div class="hl-about">
      <Highlight type="star" color="purple" pre="Tip:">
        You can navigate the sidebar using a limited set of vim motions like
        <kbd>j</kbd>, <kbd>k</kbd> and <kbd>o</kbd>
      </Highlight>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  @import "../styles/variables.scss";
  @import "../styles/mixins.scss";

  strong {
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  kbd {
    color: $accent-light;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    font-weight: 700;

    &::before {
      content: "[";
    }

    &::after {
      content: "]";
    }
  }

  .hl-about {
    @include respond-to(sm) {
      background: red;
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
